parameter.description: Maximum number of outstanding read transactions; only applicable for AXI protocol

parameter.description: Maximum number of outstanding write transactions; only applicable for AXI protocol

parameter.name: /timing/read/cmd_accept_cycles
parameter.description: Number of clock cycles to accept read command

parameter.description: Number of clock cycles to trigger first beat of read data

parameter.name: /timing/read/next_beat_cycles
parameter.description: Number of clock cycles to trigger subsequent beats of read data

parameter.name: /timing/write/cmd_accept_cycles
parameter.description: Number of clock cycles to accept write command

parameter.name: /timing/write/first_beat_cycles
parameter.description: Number of clock cycles to accept first beat of write data

parameter.name: /timing/write/next_beat_cycles
parameter.description: Number of clock cycles to accept subsequent beats of write data
